comments.content:
set_vif_bandwidth_config may get an inst_type (as its second parameter) that has no 'extra_specs' field, or an 'extra_specs' field whose value is None. This is perfectly normal, but will cause a KeyError or an AttributeError:

    for key, value in inst_type['extra_specs'].iteritems():
        ...
